Omutume Pawulo yawandiika ku kyegulo kya Mukama mu 1 Abakkolinso 11:23-29.
Pawulo amaliliza n’ebigambo ebitasangika mu Njiri: “Kyanaavanga azza omusango ogw'omubiri n'omusaayi gwa Mukama waffe buli anaalyanga ku mugaati aba anaanywanga ku kikompe kya Mukama waffe nga tasaanidde.
