Endagaanoempya (New Covenant)  yawanyisibwa n’Endagaano enkadde(Old Covenant) Kristu, Akaliga k’embaga y’okuyitako, (1 Abakkolinso 5:7), bwe kasaddakibwa (Abaebbulaniya 8:8-13).
